</h2>
<h3>
    <strong>Spinning and Casting Tips</strong>
</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        Use medium-action rods paired with spinning reels.
    </li>
    <li>
        Favorite lures: <strong>Blue Fox spinners</strong>, <strong>Mepps</strong>, and <strong>Kastmasters</strong>.
    </li>
    <li>
